        <sponsor name-id="S299">Mr. Vitter</sponsor> (for himself,
			 <cosponsor name-id="S236">Mr. Inhofe</cosponsor>, and <cosponsor name-id="S212">Mr. Coats</cosponsor>) introduced the following bill; which was
